data.meta_description: Frontiers Music Srl  -  Proud record label home to the likes of Journey, Toto, Night Ranger, Stryper, Mr. Big, Whitesnake, Winger, Sebastian Bach, California Breed, Jake E. Lee's Red Dragon Cartel, Timo Tolkki's Avalon, Pretty Maids, Yes, Asia, Ted Nugent, Primal Fear, Jorn Lande, John Waite, Neal Schon, Uriah Heep, Extreme, Heart, Electric Light Orchestra, Jeff Lynne, Chicago and many more!
